HEADWORD: metrication
<hw>met`ri*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(m⟦ecr⟧t`r⟦icr⟧*k⟦amac⟧"sh⟦ucr⟧n)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <def>The act or process of converting the standard system
